#### Use cases of Nomad Vault integration:

1. Nomad secrets Engine: The Nomad secrets engine for Vault generates Nomad ACL tokens dynamically based on pre-existing Nomad ACL policies.
https://developer.hashicorp.com/vault/docs/secrets/nomad 

2. Use workload identities with Vault: Nomad integrates with Vault to retrieve static and dynamic secrets for workloads.
https://developer.hashicorp.com/nomad/docs/secure/workload-identity/vault
https://developer.hashicorp.com/nomad/docs/concepts/workload-identity
https://developer.hashicorp.com/nomad/docs/configuration/vault#create_from_role

3. Generate mTLS certificates for Nomad using Vault: 
https://developer.hashicorp.com/nomad/tutorials/integrate-vault/vault-pki-nomad

Workflow:-
[Nomad Server]
   |
   | (management token proves identity)
   v
[Vault] <--- ACLs checked
   |
   | (issues child token with requested policies)
   v
[Nomad Client] --- knows Vault address
   |
   | (injects VAULT_TOKEN into task env)
   v
[Task] --- uses VAULT_TOKEN to access secrets



